138
00:05:12.437 --> 00:05:14.981  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:84.33% 
Nah, I’m fine.
Looks like you had a big week.

139
00:05:15.065 --> 00:05:19.110  position:55.00%,start  align:start size:40.00%  line:69.06% 
You heard about that?

140
00:05:15.065 --> 00:05:19.110  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:50.00%  line:84.23% 
