00:05:19.194 --> 00:05:21.571  position:30.00%,start  align:start size:40.00%  line:75.93% 
By the way, sincerely–

142
00:05:19.194 --> 00:05:21.571  position:80.00%,start  align:start size:15.00%  line:89.66% 
Yeah?

143
00:05:21.655 --> 00:05:23.072  position:20.00%,start  align:start size:75.00%  line:89.67% 
Great.

144
00:05:23.156 --> 00:05:25.575  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:84.33% 
Great guacamole
on the bar there.

145
00:05:28.036 --> 00:05:29.495  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:89.67% 
Wow. That’s it?

146
00:05:29.579 --> 00:05:32.373  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:79.00% 
Everything you did for him,
and he doesn’t even say
thank you?

147
00:05:32.457 --> 00:05:34.083  position:40.00%,start  align:start size:55.00%  line:89.67% 
I get it.

148
00:05:34.167 --> 00:05:36.752  position:30.00%,start  align:start size:65.00%  line:84.33% 
It’s "hero" with a "she."
Oh!

149
00:05:36.836 --> 00:05:39.589  position:55.00%,start  align:start size:40.00%  line:84.33% 
