150
00:05:39.673 --> 00:05:41.507  position:60.00%,start  align:start size:35.00%  line:89.67% 
That’s just his way.

151
00:05:41.591 --> 00:05:45.928  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:79.00% 
