How could such a terrible
mistake have occurred?

161
00:06:11.621 --> 00:06:14.040  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:79.00% 
I think she must have
just thought it was
a toy or something.

162
00:06:14.124 --> 00:06:16.042  position:25.00%,start  align:start size:70.00%  line:84.33% 
Well, I hope it’s not
completely ruined forever.

163
00:06:16.126 --> 00:06:19.253  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:79.00% 
Oh, no. Are you kidding me?
My daddy uses
a special shellac on this thing.

164
00:06:19.337 --> 00:06:22.715  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:79.00% 
This is water resistant,
heat resistant–
You name it.

165
00:06:22.799 --> 00:06:24.133  position:70.00%,start  align:start size:25.00%  line:69.06% 
Good to know.

166
00:06:22.799 --> 00:06:24.133  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:30.00%  line:84.23% 
