someplace safe.

167
00:06:24.217 --> 00:06:25.885  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:84.33% 
It could still be slippery,
so be careful.

168
00:06:25.969 --> 00:06:28.262  position:60.00%,start  align:start size:35.00%  line:79.00% 
Is it?
Oh, yeah, it is!
It’s slippery!

169
00:06:28.346 --> 00:06:29.722  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:20.00%  line:75.93% 
Is it okay?

170
00:06:28.346 --> 00:06:29.722  position:65.00%,start  align:start size:10.00%  line:89.66% 
Ah.

171
00:06:29.806 --> 00:06:32.225  position:35.00%,start  align:start size:60.00%  line:84.33% 
