- Whew.

172
00:06:32.309 --> 00:06:33.810  position:55.00%,start  align:start size:40.00%  line:84.33% 
Apparently, I’m tougher
than I look.

173
00:06:38.857 --> 00:06:41.943  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:40.00%  line:69.06% 
Hey, boys, having fun?

174
00:06:38.857 --> 00:06:41.943  position:25.00%,start  align:start size:45.00%  line:84.23% 
You know it.
Love us some Jay’s night.

175
00:06:42.027 --> 00:06:43.236  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:89.67% 
[ Chuckles ]

176
00:06:43.320 --> 00:06:44.779  position:55.00%,start  align:start size:40.00%  line:89.67% 
