177
00:06:44.863 --> 00:06:47.698  position:55.00%,start  align:start size:40.00%  line:84.33% 
Kristy Hughes,
a.k.a. Kristy Huge Ones,

178
00:06:47.782 --> 00:06:49.784  position:60.00%,start  align:start size:35.00%  line:84.33% 
is having a pool party
two blocks away.

179
00:06:49.868 --> 00:06:52.745  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:45.00%  line:70.50% 
What about Jay?
He thinks we’re at a party.

180
00:06:49.868 --> 00:06:52.745  position:65.00%,start  align:start size:30.00%  line:89.66% 
He’ll never know.

181
00:06:52.829 --> 00:06:55.498  position:30.00%,start  align:start size:65.00%  line:79.00% 
We sneak out,
work the room,
cannonball, cannonball,

182
00:06:55.582 --> 00:06:56.791  position:65.00%,start  align:start size:30.00%  line:84.33% 
and we’re back
in time for dinner.

183
00:06:56.875 --> 00:06:59.001  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:40.00%  line:75.93% 
Were you even invited?

184
00:06:56.875 --> 00:06:59.001  position:65.00%,start  align:start size:10.00%  line:89.66% 
No.

185
00:06:59.085 --> 00:07:01.754  position:55.00%,start  align:start size:40.00%  line:79.00% 
But that’s only because
I don’t know her
or any of her friends.

186
00:07:01.838 --> 00:07:03.381  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:84.33% 
We’re not invading
her house.

187
00:07:03.465 --> 00:07:05.341  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:84.33% 
And besides,
this hair at a pool party?

188
00:07:05.425 --> 00:07:08.178  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:84.33% 
One dunk and it goes off
like an air bag. Poof!

189
00:07:12.057 --> 00:07:13.599  position:10.00%,start  align:start size:85.00%  line:84.33% 
What’s this?
You made sauce?

190
00:07:13.683 --> 00:07:16.102  position:60.00%,start  align:start size:35.00%  line:79.00% 
Well, you were sick.
I didn’t know
if you could handle it.

191
00:07:16.186 --> 00:07:18.437  position:10.00%,start  align:start size:85.00%  line:84.33% 
Back in Vietnam,
I had hepatitis.

192
00:07:18.521 --> 00:07:21.566  position:30.00%,start  align:start size:65.00%  line:79.00% 
Still managed to cook
Thanksgiving dinner
for 300 soldiers.

193
00:07:21.650 --> 00:07:23.109  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:89.67% 
I think I can handle sauce.

194
00:07:23.193 --> 00:07:25.278  position:65.00%,start  align:start size:30.00%  line:84.33% 
Well, I saved you
the trouble.

195
00:07:25.362 --> 00:07:28.281  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:84.33% 
So Margaret tells me I’m using
some new delivery trucks now.

196
00:07:28.365 --> 00:07:30.283  position:70.00%,start  align:start size:25.00%  line:84.33% 
Yeah.
They’re hybrid.

197
00:07:30.367 --> 00:07:31.742  position:70.00%,start  align:start size:25.00%  line:84.33% 
Now, they cost
a little more,

198
00:07:31.826 --> 00:07:34.704  position:55.00%,start  align:start size:40.00%  line:79.00% 
but when I factored in
the tax rebates you get
for going green,

199
00:07:34.788 --> 00:07:36.289  position:30.00%,start  align:start size:65.00%  line:89.67% 
we come out ahead.

200
00:07:36.373 --> 00:07:38.541  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:79.00% 
Speaking of green,
you went a little heavy
on the vegetables, huh?

201
00:07:38.625 --> 00:07:40.876  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:84.33% 
I’m not sure I can stomach
anything that’s healthy.

202
00:07:40.960 --> 00:07:43.879  position:25.00%,start  align:start size:70.00%  line:73.67% 
Gosh, Mom, that truck thing
sounds so amazing.
 
Yeah.

203
00:07:43.963 --> 00:07:46.215  position:70.00%,start  align:start size:25.00%  line:84.33% 
Uh, uh, uh–
It’s fine, Dad.

204
00:07:46.299 --> 00:07:48.342  position:60.00%,start  align:start size:35.00%  line:84.33% 
Only do what we’re
capable of, right?

205
00:07:48.426 --> 00:07:50.886  position:30.00%,start  align:start size:65.00%  line:84.33% 
Oh– No, Stella, stay.
No.

206
00:07:50.970 --> 00:07:53.389  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:84.33% 
Good girl.
Thank you, Stella.

207
00:07:53.473 --> 00:07:55.433  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:89.67% 
Thank you for listening.

208
00:07:56.559 --> 00:08:00.397  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:84.33% 
Oh, I’m so proud of you.
Who’s my best girl?

209
00:08:02.816 --> 00:08:04.150  position:45.00%,start  align:start size:50.00%  line:89.67% 
Don’t.

210
00:08:04.234 --> 00:08:06.485  position:25.00%,start  align:start size:70.00%  line:84.33% 
Okay, girls,
we are ready for Scrabble.

211
00:08:06.569 --> 00:08:08.696  position:25.00%,start  align:start size:70.00%  line:84.33% 
- I’ll grab some snacks.
- Oh, potato chips, please.

212
00:08:08.780 --> 00:08:11.783  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:79.00% 
Oh, so I can hear
about how much
you hate yourself all night?

213
00:08:18.081 --> 00:08:19.582  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:89.67% 
Hello, Luke.

214
00:08:19.666 --> 00:08:21.125  position:10.00%,start  align:start size:85.00%  line:84.33% 
Oh, come on.
We’ve gotta go.

215
00:08:21.209 --> 00:08:22.752  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:84.33% 
That party’s full
of sophomores.

216
00:08:22.836 --> 00:08:24.545  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:45.00%  line:75.93% 
Those women have lived.

217
00:08:22.836 --> 00:08:24.545  position:65.00%,start  align:start size:10.00%  line:89.66% 
No.

218
00:08:24.629 --> 00:08:27.715  position:25.00%,start  align:start size:70.00%  line:79.00% 
We’re going back inside,
we’re eating Jay’s food
and playing his board games.

219
00:08:27.799 --> 00:08:30.343  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:40.00%  line:69.06% 
More like boring games.

220
00:08:27.799 --> 00:08:30.343  position:70.00%,start  align:start size:25.00%  line:84.23% 
They’re already
called "board."

221
00:08:30.427 --> 00:08:32.595  position:65.00%,start  align:start size:30.00%  line:79.00% 
You don’t make it
more clever by–
Never mind.

222
00:08:36.433 --> 00:08:38.059  position:35.00%,start  align:start size:60.00%  line:89.67% 
Okay, thanks.

223
00:08:38.143 --> 00:08:40.061  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:84.33% 
