with the wedding singer?

224
00:08:40.145 --> 00:08:42.855  position:25.00%,start  align:start size:70.00%  line:79.00% 
Oh, yeah. I’m just dropping
my big finale because
he’s doing the same song.

225
00:08:42.939 --> 00:08:44.690  position:15.00%,start  align:start size:20.00%  line:75.93% 
"My Way"?

226
00:08:42.939 --> 00:08:44.690  position:65.00%,start  align:start size:15.00%  line:89.66% 
His way.

227
00:08:44.774 --> 00:08:47.485  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:79.00% 
Hey, guys.
Sorry we’re late,
but we come with wine.

228
00:08:47.569 --> 00:08:49.737  position:35.00%,start  align:start size:25.00%  line:75.93% 
And whittlin’.

229
00:08:47.569 --> 00:08:49.737  position:65.00%,start  align:start size:10.00%  line:89.66% 
Oh!

230
00:08:49.821 --> 00:08:52.323  position:30.00%,start  align:start size:65.00%  line:79.00% 
