my father made...

231
00:08:52.407 --> 00:08:54.075  position:55.00%,start  align:start size:40.00%  line:84.33% 
for the top
of our wedding cake.

232
00:08:54.159 --> 00:08:56.702  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:84.33% 
