before he got to me.

233
00:08:56.786 --> 00:08:58.454  position:65.00%,start  align:start size:10.00%  line:75.93% 
Darn.

234
00:08:56.786 --> 00:08:58.454  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:15.00%  line:89.66% 
For you.

235
00:08:58.538 --> 00:09:01.707  position:35.00%,start  align:start size:60.00%  line:79.00% 
