Cam’s the damsel.

242
00:09:12.427 --> 00:09:14.804  position:20.00%,start  align:start size:10.00%  line:89.66% 
Dad!

243
00:09:15.680 --> 00:09:17.306  position:15.00%,start  align:start size:80.00%  line:89.67% 
Thank you.

244
00:09:17.390 --> 00:09:19.350  position:65.00%,start  align:start size:30.00%  line:84.33% 
A lot can happen
before the big day.

245
00:09:19.434 --> 00:09:22.144  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:84.33% 
Believe me,
I’ve already tried.

246
00:09:22.228 --> 00:09:23.646  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:89.67% 
That thing is indestructible.

247
00:09:23.730 --> 00:09:25.898  position:65.00%,start  align:start size:30.00%  line:84.33% 
Hmm. What if
it went missing?

248
00:09:25.982 --> 00:09:28.150  position:65.00%,start  align:start size:30.00%  line:79.00% 
