around here
all the time.

249
00:09:28.234 --> 00:09:29.443  position:20.00%,start  align:start size:75.00%  line:89.67% 
Do they?

250
00:09:29.527 --> 00:09:30.611  position:25.00%,start  align:start size:5.00%  line:75.93% 
Hi.

251
00:09:29.527 --> 00:09:30.611  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:10.00%  line:89.66% 
Hey.

252
00:09:30.695 --> 00:09:32.988  position:75.00%,start  align:start size:20.00%  line:89.67% 
All the time.

253
00:09:33.072 --> 00:09:36.867  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:79.00% 
Let’s just say
I have a friend who helps me
in these kinds of situations.

254
00:09:36.951 --> 00:09:38.953  position:15.00%,start  align:start size:25.00%  line:69.06% 
I’m listening.

255
00:09:36.951 --> 00:09:38.953  position:60.00%,start  align:start size:35.00%  line:84.23% 
