the better.

256
00:09:39.037 --> 00:09:40.746  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:89.67% 
I’m not listening.

257
00:09:40.830 --> 00:09:42.331  position:35.00%,start  align:start size:60.00%  line:84.33% 
We never had
this conversation.

258
00:09:42.415 --> 00:09:43.666  position:30.00%,start  align:start size:65.00%  line:89.67% 
