259
00:09:43.750 --> 00:09:45.126  position:65.00%,start  align:start size:30.00%  line:89.67% 
Right.

260
00:09:45.210 --> 00:09:47.128  position:60.00%,start  align:start size:35.00%  line:89.67% 
I am giving you the...

