270
00:10:11.361 --> 00:10:14.155  position:65.00%,start  align:start size:30.00%  line:84.33% 
Hey, who are you
really mad at?

271
00:10:14.239 --> 00:10:15.573  position:10.00%,start  align:start size:85.00%  line:89.67% 
